2ï¸âƒ£ Backtracking (DFS) â†’ Iterates through available characters, forming unique sequences by decrementing the count, recursively exploring further, and restoring counts after recursion.
3ï¸âƒ£ Summing Up Possibilities â†’ Every valid sequence is counted as a possibility.

âœ… No need for sorting or permutationsâ€”this method efficiently generates all possibilities while avoiding duplicates.

ğŸ’¡ Time Complexity: O(âˆ‘ (factorial of character counts)), but optimized using pruning.

